 COLD SDS and disconnect the Service jumper. 
</p></li><li id="LI_50E213EF99904105955A3A2C23FCE763" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the top cover. 
</p><note type="important" id="GUID-7215619B-4D8E-42B1-B219-10C1EF6B5FB5" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Do not lean on the strip support. 
</p></note></li><li id="LI_B3070DDF7AFE4B65BF4A8343C06C58BE" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the maintenance tray. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="07DISA020" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-C04E8AED-532E-4792-9B1F-478E74979222.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 07 How to remove the maintenance tray?>07 How to remove the maintenance tray</xref> 
</p></li><li id="LI_8EFCF849C54841B08EA90E712816C8E3" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the maintenance tray assembly. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="07DISA022" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-2D90D262-D1D0-4062-B2F5-28ED447BF111.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 07 How to remove the maintenance tray assembly?>07 How to remove the maintenance tray assembly</xref> 
</p></li><li id="LI_4A5292BCDE6D4A1F8BF3EC341C13C4BB" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the maintenance unit. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="07DISA024" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-17B27C06-4881-45FC-A784-579CC398D058.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 07 How to remove the maintenance unit?>07 How to remove the Tissue Wipe Unit</xref> 
